Manifesting my Japan trip from home, one ritual at a time 🇯🇵🍵🎋

First up — always matcha. It’s my everyday essential, my moment of calm 💚

Japanese skincare? Unmatched. I’ve been loving @claycobeauty ’s SunGlaze Sunscreen — inspired by Japanese tech, lightweight, and now a non-negotiable in my routine ☁️🧴

And as someone who swears by the Wabi-Sabi mindset, I’m learning to find beauty in the in-between — the pauses, the stillness, the soft 🌸✨

It’s not just a vibe—it’s a ritual 🍵✨

Using a chawan (matcha bowl) and a bamboo whisk holder isn’t “extra”—it’s how you get that smooth, frothy, barista-style matcha at home.
The bowl gives you the right shape for whisking, and the holder keeps your whisk in perfect form 💚

Trust me, your matcha will thank you.
